user.biography: A Place Like No Other™. Home to 71 rides, including 18 roller coasters, Cedar Point Shores Waterpark and more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on August 01, 2021. May be an image of french fries.

node.text:
Cedar Point is famous for our fresh-cut fries, but you HAVE to try them during Taste of the Point going on now through Aug. 15!

Check out the whole menu and get your tasting card here: bit.ly/3x9iAcJ

node.text:
Keep arms down, head back and hold on. 🚦 
Vroom! Vrooooom! 🏁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 30, 2021.

node.text:
Hooray - it's Fan Fri-YAY! 😄 Today's exclusive button is all about Snake River Expedition - our new boat ride that takes you on an epic adventure through the wildly inhabited lagoons in the park. 🐍 

Get your limited-edition button only at Button Stop along the Main Midway!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 28, 2021. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
It's #NationalWaterparkDay! Celebrate at Cedar Point Shores with an exhilarating plummet down one of our awesome water slides, chilling in Cedar Creek lazy river or making waves in the 500,000-gallon Breakwater Bay! 🌊

It's the perfect mix of adventure and relaxation! 😌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, outdoors and text.

node.text:
We've hit another milestone! 😄 

Congratulations to Victoria all the way from Crawfordville, Florida for being the 500,000th rider this season on Magnum XL-200! 🎢

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 24, 2021. May be an image of dessert and text that says 'SWEE Ceda Point's SPOT ELIZABETH KELSEY macarons'.

node.text:
No, but really... have you tried a Kelsey Elizabeth macaron?!?! 😋 

This is one tasty treat that you HAVE to try while you're at Cedar Point! Find tons of flavors in Sweet Spot, including the 150 Celebration vanilla bean macaron! 😍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 23, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Happy #FanFriday! We're showcasing this vintage design for this week's button release. You can ONLY find this gem 💎 at Button Stop along the Main Midway while supplies last!

node.text:
You have to see Celebrate 150 Spectacular to believe it! 💗 

Every night until August 15, experience a celebration that only comes around every 150 years. The Fun is just Beginning.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 21, 2021.

node.text: Find this week's limited-edition pin in Frontier Studio along the Frontier Trail today!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'h & CREATIONS GLASS THEATER BLOWING HAND D-MA UNIQUE SOUVENIRS'.

node.text:
If rides and roller coasters aren't your thing, there's still plenty to do and see at Cedar Point! 😄 

Enjoy daily shows at the Glass Blowing Theatre where talented artisans demonstrate how to make beautiful creations made entirely out of glass!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 5 people, people standing and text that says 'YEARS YEARS'.

node.text:
Have you seen the Celebrate 150 Spectacular show yet? 👀 

Take a journey through Cedar Point's history with live music, dancers, singers and performers galore! The fun starts at 9:30 p.m. in Celebration Plaza every night through August 15! 🙌 
#TheFunisJustBeginning

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Cedar Point 150 YEARS'.

node.text: Happy #FanFriday! Get your exclusive button this week at The Button Stop along the Main Midway while supplies last!
